data.description: Discover your dream home in Mesquite's most delightful neighborhood! This charming abode, after a heart-stealing renovation, exudes adorable appeal. The kitchen boasts sleek stone countertops, new appliances, and a sprinkle of culinary magic. The renovated restrooms seamlessly blend relaxation with sophistication. Explore this cozy 3-bedroom, 2-bath haven and feel the warmth of beautiful wood floors underfoot. This isn't just a house; it's a love-filled home. Freshly painted walls embrace you, and a rare treasure awaits—a full two-car detached garage and two driveways, ending parking struggles and embracing ultimate convenience. Fall head over heels for this well-maintained masterpiece; it's a unicorn in the housing market. Act fast, find your happy place, and embark on a new chapter in your life.
